1
00:00:01,780 --> 00:00:04,139
<Default><b>[wind sound]</b></Default>

2
00:00:11,919 --> 00:00:14,099
<Default><b>[♪ Melancholic music]</b></Default>

3
00:00:34,340 --> 00:00:35,177
<Default><b>{\i1}Jaralis.{\i0}</b></Default>

4
00:00:35,201 --> 00:00:36,866
<Default><b>{\i1}Our supply lines{\i0}
{\i1}have been cut off{\i0}</b></Default>

5
00:00:36,890 --> 00:00:39,176
<Default><b>[SOLDIER] {\i1}with no chance{\i0}
{\i1}of reinforcements.{\i0}</b></Default>

6
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:41,440
<Default><b>[SOLDIER] {\i1} I'm afraid{\i0}
{\i1}there's no hope.{\i0}</b></Default>

7
00:00:44,670 --> 00:00:46,109
<Default><b>{\i1}So this is it.{\i0}</b></Default>

8
00:00:48,399 --> 00:00:50,509
<Default><b>[♪ Dramatic music]</b></Default>

9
00:00:57,799 --> 00:00:59,240
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

10
00:01:01,549 --> 00:01:02,780
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

11
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:15,305
<Default><b>[SOLDIER]{\i1} Jaralis, give us{\i0}
{\i1}the order to retreat!{\i0}</b></Default>

12
00:01:15,329 --> 00:01:17,009
<Default><b>[SOLDIER] {\i1}Jaralis, sir!{\i0}</b></Default>

13
00:01:21,010 --> 00:01:22,805
<Default><b>{\i1}All right, my
fellow warriors.{\i0}</b></Default>

14
00:01:22,829 --> 00:01:25,069
<Default><b>{\i1}Time to show them{\i0}
{\i1}what you're made of.{\i0}</b></Default>

15
00:01:25,379 --> 00:01:28,510
<Default><b>{\i1}If we fail to defeat the rebels{\i0}
{\i1}here on this battlefield</b></Default>

16
00:01:28,569 --> 00:01:31,169
<Default><b>{\i1}they will not stop{\i0}
{\i1}until they reach the castle.{\i0}</b></Default>

17
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:35,585
<Default><b>[JARALIS] {\i1}For the unification{\i0}
{\i1}of our homeland.{\i0}</b></Default>

18
00:01:35,609 --> 00:01:37,049
<Default><b>{\i1}And our comrades!{\i0}</b></Default>

19
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,885
<Default><b>{\i1}You, brave soldier</b></Default>

20
00:01:39,909 --> 00:01:42,069
<Default><b>{\i1}to prevent the advance{\i0}
{\i1}of the enemy.{\i0}</b></Default>

21
00:01:42,709 --> 00:01:43,829
<Default><b>{\i1}All rise!{\i0}</b></Default>

22
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:46,180
<Default><b>[hesitation]</b></Default>

23
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:48,230
<Default><b>{\i1}Ready?{\i0}</b></Default>

24
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,579
<Default><b>{\i1}And now, charge!{\i0}</b></Default>

25
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:53,420
<Default><b>[soldiers roaring]</b></Default>

26
00:01:56,459 --> 00:01:59,066
<Default><b>{\i1}Well, at the very least</b></Default>

27
00:01:59,090 --> 00:02:01,945
<Default><b>{\i1}As for me, I must stay alive{\i0}
{\i1}to see this through.{\i0}</b></Default>

28
00:02:01,969 --> 00:02:04,605
<Default><b>[SOLDIER] {\i1}It's Tiran!{\i0}
{\i1}His reinforcements have arrived.{\i0}</b></Default>

29
00:02:04,629 --> 00:02:05,400
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

30
00:02:05,629 --> 00:02:08,930
<Default><b>[soldiers roaring]</b></Default>

31
00:02:11,719 --> 00:02:12,726
<Default><b>{\i1}Take courage!{\i0}</b></Default>

32
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:15,545
<Default><b>{\i1}And we'll show them{\i0}
{\i1}we're the pride of Siltvelt.{\i0}</b></Default>

33
00:02:15,569 --> 00:02:17,129
<Default><b>[SOLDIERS] {\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}</b></Default>

34
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,340
<Default><b>{\i1}Tiran.{\i0}</b></Default>

35
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,360
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

36
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:26,039
<Default><b>[gong]</b></Default>

37
00:02:27,699 --> 00:02:28,819
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

38
00:02:33,090 --> 00:02:35,370
<Default><b>Those accursed eyes
are so familiar.</b></Default>

39
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:38,939
<Default><b>[♪ Opening music begins]</b></Default>

40
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:47,009
<Default><b>THE RISING OF
THE SHIELD HERO</b></Default>

41
00:04:02,979 --> 00:04:05,479
<Default><b>[♪ opening music ends]</b></Default>

42
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:10,560
<Default><b>EPISODE 4:
ENTRUSTED POWER</b></Default>

43
00:04:10,810 --> 00:04:15,430
<Default><b>[♪ dramatic music]</b></Default>

44
00:04:16,370 --> 00:04:17,490
<Default><b>[scream]</b></Default>

45
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:24,120
<Default><b>The Minotaur with the axe
has quite a shine for Atla.</b></Default>

46
00:04:24,250 --> 00:04:25,985
<Default><b>It's just so
frustrating.</b></Default>

47
00:04:26,009 --> 00:04:28,329
<Default><b>All we can do now
is watch what happens.</b></Default>

48
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:33,860
<Default><b>For now, we'll just have
to place our faith in them.</b></Default>

49
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:37,425
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

50
00:04:37,449 --> 00:04:38,209
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

51
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:39,206
<Default><b>[scream]</b></Default>

52
00:04:39,230 --> 00:04:40,350
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

53
00:04:41,420 --> 00:04:42,980
<Default><b>Nothing but a brat.</b></Default>

54
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:45,090
<Default><b>[exhalation]</b></Default>

55
00:04:47,370 --> 00:04:49,730
<Default><b>[scream]</b></Default>

56
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:53,780
<Default><b>You never leave
an opening during a duel.</b></Default>

57
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:57,270
<Default><b>Oh, that wasn't
an opening.</b></Default>

58
00:04:57,670 --> 00:05:00,589
<Default><b>[battle scream]</b></Default>

59
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:06,019
<Default><b>{\i1}He has speed</b></Default>

60
00:05:06,459 --> 00:05:07,519
<Default><b>{\i1}Maybe{\i0}…</b></Default>

61
00:05:17,490 --> 00:05:20,055
<Default><b>[JARALIS] You really thought
you could defeat me?</b></Default>

62
00:05:20,079 --> 00:05:21,500
<Default><b>Child!</b></Default>

63
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:24,100
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

64
00:05:25,139 --> 00:05:26,600
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

65
00:05:32,769 --> 00:05:33,569
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

66
00:05:33,779 --> 00:05:35,226
<Default><b>Is that all you've got?</b></Default>

67
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:37,350
<Default><b>In the end</b></Default>

68
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:39,050
<Default><b>[grunt]</b></Default>

69
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,105
<Default><b>[scream]</b></Default>

70
00:05:40,129 --> 00:05:41,169
<Default><b>[groan]</b></Default>

71
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:48,665
<Default><b>How's it going?
You all right, brother?</b></Default>

72
00:05:48,689 --> 00:05:49,500
<Default><b>Oh, yeah.</b></Default>

73
00:05:49,689 --> 00:05:52,889
<Default><b>Compared to our training back
in the village, this is nothing.</b></Default>

74
00:05:53,149 --> 00:05:54,189
<Default><b>[grunt]</b></Default>

75
00:05:55,459 --> 00:05:56,896
<Default><b>[deep exhalation]</b></Default>

76
00:05:56,920 --> 00:06:02,910
<Default><b>[combat sounds]</b></Default>

77
00:06:10,329 --> 00:06:11,980
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

78
00:06:14,449 --> 00:06:15,217
<Default><b>Interesting.</b></Default>

79
00:06:15,241 --> 00:06:17,105
<Default><b>You're much sturdier
than I tthought.</b></Default>

80
00:06:17,129 --> 00:06:19,529
<Default><b>I figured you would have
gone down by now.</b></Default>

81
00:06:20,089 --> 00:06:21,089
<Default><b>[sigh]</b></Default>

82
00:06:21,459 --> 00:06:22,625
<Default><b>It's been a long time</b></Default>

83
00:06:22,649 --> 00:06:25,689
<Default><b>since any warrior has made
my blood run so hot.</b></Default>

84
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:27,690
<Default><b>This will be fun.</b></Default>

85
00:06:28,290 --> 00:06:29,370
<Default><b>Come on.</b></Default>

86
00:06:29,670 --> 00:06:31,959
<Default><b>Entertain me some more!</b></Default>

87
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:35,000
<Default><b>Show them, Lyceras</b></Default>

88
00:06:35,180 --> 00:06:38,230
<Default><b>Go, Jarlis! Bring judgment
on those tainted tigers!</b></Default>

89
00:06:38,389 --> 00:06:41,309
<Default><b>Hey Filo, we must cheer
for them really loud right now!</b></Default>

90
00:06:41,540 --> 00:06:42,060
<Default><b>Yep.</b></Default>

91
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,560
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

92
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:46,589
<Default><b>Go, Atla! You
can do it! Woo!</b></Default>

93
00:06:46,670 --> 00:06:47,670
<Default><b>Yeah!</b></Default>

94
00:06:48,189 --> 00:06:50,185
<Default><b>Oh, Fohl. If you win</b></Default>

95
00:06:50,209 --> 00:06:53,125
<Default><b>I'll make sure to thank you
for being such a good boy.</b></Default>

96
00:06:53,149 --> 00:06:54,269
<Default><b>[stammer]</b></Default>

97
00:06:55,009 --> 00:06:55,777
<Default><b>[cough]</b></Default>

98
00:06:55,801 --> 00:06:56,921
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

99
00:06:57,139 --> 00:06:58,139
<Default><b>Oh no.</b></Default>

100
00:06:58,810 --> 00:07:01,315
<Default><b>[ATLA] Brother! As soon as
I'm done with this guy</b></Default>

101
00:07:01,339 --> 00:07:03,339
<Default><b>I'd be happy
to take your place.</b></Default>

102
00:07:03,449 --> 00:07:05,689
<Default><b>[FOHL] I'll finish this
before you do!</b></Default>

103
00:07:06,769 --> 00:07:09,329
<Default><b>Takes me back watching
those youngsters fight.</b></Default>

104
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:10,755
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

105
00:07:10,779 --> 00:07:13,490
<Default><b>Ah yes, like when I used
to watch Tiran fight.</b></Default>

106
00:07:13,529 --> 00:07:14,529
<Default><b>[gasp]</b></Default>

107
00:07:15,990 --> 00:07:18,040
<Default><b>Yes, I can see it too.</b></Default>

108
00:07:18,110 --> 00:07:20,190
<Default><b>And he has
the same spirit in him.</b></Default>

109
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:22,900
<Default><b>Who's this Tiran guy
you're talking about?</b></Default>

110
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:25,399
<Default><b>He's the father
of Atla and Fohl.</b></Default>

111
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:27,175
<Default><b>[ETHAN] Well he was.</b></Default>

112
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:29,120
<Default><b>[♪ Music with flute]</b></Default>

113
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:31,020
<Default><b>Their father?</b></Default>

114
00:07:31,209 --> 00:07:31,990
<Default><b>[ELDER] Yes.</b></Default>

115
00:07:32,029 --> 00:07:34,230
<Default><b>Tiran, son of
King Tyran.</b></Default>

116
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:37,930
<Default><b>The powerful king of the race
of the white tiger Demi-humans</b></Default>

117
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:41,350
<Default><b>here in Siltvelt</b></Default>

118
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:46,939
<Default><b>[ELDER] His talents succeeded
even those of the former king.</b></Default>

119
00:07:47,189 --> 00:07:50,220
<Default><b>[ELDER] Yet he tried to avoid
combat at all costs.</b></Default>

120
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:54,680
<Default><b>[ELDER] Thus, he and
the last king did not get along.</b></Default>

121
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,620
<Default><b>[ELDER] And he was expelled
from the family.</b></Default>

122
00:08:00,259 --> 00:08:02,600
<Default><b>[old door closing]</b></Default>

123
00:08:07,470 --> 00:08:09,216
<Default><b>[ELDER] After
Tyran's death</b></Default>

124
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:11,839
<Default><b>rebellion broke out
all over the nation.</b></Default>

125
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:14,480
<Default><b>[ELDER] I'm told
that Tyran and Jaralis</b></Default>

126
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:16,999
<Default><b>even fought together
to quell the rebellion.</b></Default>

127
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,910
<Default><b>[♪ Intense
dramatic music]</b></Default>

128
00:08:19,949 --> 00:08:22,269
<Default><b>[scream]</b></Default>

129
00:08:25,649 --> 00:08:26,889
<Default><b>You're mine!</b></Default>

130
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:33,830
<Default><b>[battle screams]</b></Default>

131
00:08:36,610 --> 00:08:37,610
<Default><b>[gasp]</b></Default>

132
00:08:39,779 --> 00:08:40,659
<Default><b>[gasp]</b></Default>

133
00:08:40,710 --> 00:08:41,950
<Default><b>[exhalation]</b></Default>

134
00:08:42,259 --> 00:08:44,755
<Default><b>He probably won't be able
to stand for a bit.</b></Default>

135
00:08:44,779 --> 00:08:46,899
<Default><b>You see</b></Default>

136
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,720
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

137
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:51,299
<Default><b>I'm not done yet!</b></Default>

138
00:08:54,889 --> 00:08:56,755
<Default><b>I can tell you're
a seasoned warrior.</b></Default>

139
00:08:56,779 --> 00:08:59,875
<Default><b>And you're not going to let me
defeat you that easily, are you?</b></Default>

140
00:08:59,899 --> 00:09:02,070
<Default><b>You have the bearing
of royal blood.</b></Default>

141
00:09:02,350 --> 00:09:05,046
<Default><b>So is it his blood
that makes you so bold?</b></Default>

142
00:09:05,070 --> 00:09:05,779
<Default><b>Lyceras!</b></Default>

143
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:08,310
<Default><b>Why is it taking you
so long to defeat her?</b></Default>

144
00:09:08,429 --> 00:09:09,476
<Default><b>[FOHL] Eyes on me!</b></Default>

145
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,279
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

146
00:09:11,740 --> 00:09:12,980
<Default><b>Little brat!</b></Default>

147
00:09:13,549 --> 00:09:15,090
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

148
00:09:15,490 --> 00:09:17,100
<Default><b>Why? You're nobody.</b></Default>

149
00:09:19,190 --> 00:09:20,230
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

150
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,640
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

151
00:09:22,690 --> 00:09:23,447
<Default><b>Lyceras!</b></Default>

152
00:09:23,471 --> 00:09:26,399
<Default><b>Finish her off already
and come help me over here!</b></Default>

153
00:09:27,850 --> 00:09:29,620
<Default><b>Hey! Lyceras!</b></Default>

154
00:09:29,889 --> 00:09:31,395
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Starting to panic?</b></Default>

155
00:09:31,419 --> 00:09:32,459
<Default><b>[grunt]</b></Default>

156
00:09:32,629 --> 00:09:34,586
<Default><b>You need somebody else
to save your ass</b></Default>

157
00:09:34,610 --> 00:09:36,515
<Default><b>cause your dirty tricks
weren't enough.</b></Default>

158
00:09:36,539 --> 00:09:38,690
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I
bet the truth hurts</b></Default>

159
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:41,056
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I'm gonna
make this clear</b></Default>

160
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:43,280
<Default><b>so you can't talk
your way out of it.</b></Default>

161
00:09:43,830 --> 00:09:47,379
<Default><b>If we win, you're going to obey
whatever orders we lay down.</b></Default>

162
00:09:48,110 --> 00:09:50,070
<Default><b>You're a man
of your word</b></Default>

163
00:09:51,919 --> 00:09:53,296
<Default><b>You don't have to worry.</b></Default>

164
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:56,190
<Default><b>No one can overturn the results
of a sacred duel.</b></Default>

165
00:09:56,259 --> 00:09:57,696
<Default><b>No matter who they are.</b></Default>

166
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,600
<Default><b>The terms are
unchanging.</b></Default>

167
00:09:59,629 --> 00:10:02,025
<Default><b>That means you're preparing
a ship to Q'ten Lo</b></Default>

168
00:10:02,049 --> 00:10:03,969
<Default><b>for us to travel
in, correct?</b></Default>

169
00:10:05,309 --> 00:10:07,589
<Default><b>Then it's official.
We're in agreement.</b></Default>

170
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:10,025
<Default><b>[grunt]</b></Default>

171
00:10:10,049 --> 00:10:11,409
<Default><b>[FOHL] Jaralis!</b></Default>

172
00:10:12,419 --> 00:10:14,600
<Default><b>Don't you forget
our deal either.</b></Default>

173
00:10:14,889 --> 00:10:17,429
<Default><b>[♪ Intense,
battle music]</b></Default>

174
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,340
<Default><b>Now it appears
it's time to end this.</b></Default>

175
00:10:22,610 --> 00:10:23,770
<Default><b>Good then.</b></Default>

176
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:27,149
<Default><b>I'm going to hit you with
the strongest technique I have.</b></Default>

177
00:10:34,070 --> 00:10:35,510
<Default><b>Secret technique.</b></Default>

178
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:38,269
<Default><b>Big Bull Charge!</b></Default>

179
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:43,309
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

180
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:48,029
<Default><b>My imitation
of Hengen Musou Style.</b></Default>

181
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:51,049
<Default><b>[battle scream]</b></Default>

182
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,190
<Default><b>Jewel!</b></Default>

183
00:11:00,940 --> 00:11:02,230
<Default><b>Well done…</b></Default>

184
00:11:02,659 --> 00:11:05,120
<Default><b>Heir… of Tyran.</b></Default>

185
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:14,940
<Default><b>My dear father</b></Default>

186
00:11:15,549 --> 00:11:18,559
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

187
00:11:19,149 --> 00:11:20,189
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

188
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,080
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

189
00:11:22,129 --> 00:11:24,570
<Default><b>Hengen Musou Style</b></Default>

190
00:11:24,779 --> 00:11:26,275
<Default><b>Destroying Tiger...</b></Default>

191
00:11:26,299 --> 00:11:27,730
<Default><b>[hard breathing]</b></Default>

192
00:11:27,929 --> 00:11:29,090
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

193
00:11:29,659 --> 00:11:30,587
<Default><b>No, Fohl!</b></Default>

194
00:11:30,611 --> 00:11:33,145
<Default><b>What happened? He looks like
he's in so much pain.</b></Default>

195
00:11:33,169 --> 00:11:34,169
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

196
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,319
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

197
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,160
<Default><b>[Naofumi] Poison?</b></Default>

198
00:11:40,610 --> 00:11:42,159
<Default><b>[♪ Violin music]</b></Default>

199
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:44,769
<Default><b>Well, that worked
like a charm</b></Default>

200
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,320
<Default><b>That is so unfair!</b></Default>

201
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:49,846
<Default><b>This has to be against
the rules, right?</b></Default>

202
00:11:49,870 --> 00:11:50,580
<Default><b>Oh no.</b></Default>

203
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:53,610
<Default><b>In any of our historic
Siltvelt duels</b></Default>

204
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:55,990
<Default><b>the last one standing
is the winner.</b></Default>

205
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:58,720
<Default><b>[ELDER] According to
the rules, it's allowed.</b></Default>

206
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:01,000
<Default><b>You've got to
be kidding me!</b></Default>

207
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:02,750
<Default><b>[FOHL] Shield Hero!</b></Default>

208
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,056
<Default><b>[hard breathing]</b></Default>

209
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,200
<Default><b>I'm fine.</b></Default>

210
00:12:05,559 --> 00:12:07,139
<Default><b>I can still fight.</b></Default>

211
00:12:07,570 --> 00:12:08,576
<Default><b>[harsh inhale]</b></Default>

212
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,735
<Default><b>You can rest now
from the battle, brother.</b></Default>

213
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:12,306
<Default><b>For I will fight
on your behalf.</b></Default>

214
00:12:12,330 --> 00:12:13,570
<Default><b>[FOHL] Atla!</b></Default>

215
00:12:14,090 --> 00:12:15,610
<Default><b>I will defeat him.</b></Default>

216
00:12:16,789 --> 00:12:18,566
<Default><b>[FOHL] If I
can't defeat him</b></Default>

217
00:12:18,590 --> 00:12:21,070
<Default><b>[FOHL] I'll never hear
