218
00:12:21,799 --> 00:12:23,556
<Default><b>Oh, there's nothing
much to tell.</b></Default>

219
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:25,796
<Default><b>Your father brought
shame to Siltvelt</b></Default>

220
00:12:25,820 --> 00:12:28,269
<Default><b>by fleeing it when confronted
