223
00:12:33,259 --> 00:12:34,789
<Default><b>Sacrificing his men</b></Default>

224
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:37,970
<Default><b>just to guarantee his own
personal survival.</b></Default>

225
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,456
<Default><b>You're lying!</b></Default>

226
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,956
<Default><b>[JARALIS] I
speak the truth.</b></Default>

227
00:12:40,980 --> 00:12:42,346
<Default><b>[JARALIS] He
was no warrior.</b></Default>

228
00:12:42,370 --> 00:12:43,410
<Default><b>[grunt]</b></Default>

229
00:12:43,710 --> 00:12:46,250
<Default><b>And then he died
so pathetically.</b></Default>

230
00:12:46,379 --> 00:12:48,579
<Default><b>He was actually begging
