231
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:51,090
<Default><b>Hust shut up!</b></Default>

232
00:12:51,389 --> 00:12:52,429
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

233
00:12:53,620 --> 00:12:55,220
<Default><b>{\i1}What's with this kid?{\i0}</b></Default>

234
00:12:55,289 --> 00:12:57,330
<Default><b>{\i1}He was almost dead {\i0}
{\i1} second ago.{\i0}</b></Default>

235
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:58,496
<Default><b>You're lying!</b></Default>

236
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,429
<Default><b>Liar!</b></Default>

237
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:01,620
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

238
00:13:01,710 --> 00:13:02,587
<Default><b>{\i1}Tiran?{\i0}</b></Default>

239
00:13:02,611 --> 00:13:05,360
<Default><b>[Fohl roars]</b></Default>

240
00:13:07,580 --> 00:13:08,700
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

241
00:13:09,409 --> 00:13:11,960
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

242
00:13:12,279 --> 00:13:13,909
<Default><b>Now take it back.</b></Default>

243
00:13:14,330 --> 00:13:15,450
<Default><b>Admit it!</b></Default>

244
00:13:15,980 --> 00:13:17,500
<Default><b>He wasn't a coward!</b></Default>

245
00:13:21,460 --> 00:13:24,710
<Default><b>[evil laughter]</b></Default>

246
00:13:25,169 --> 00:13:27,809
<Default><b>Well then, if you want
to know that badly</b></Default>

247
00:13:28,009 --> 00:13:30,049
<Default><b>[JARALIS] I'm
going to tell you…</b></Default>

248
00:13:31,169 --> 00:13:33,470
<Default><b>How your
father really died.</b></Default>

249
00:13:38,250 --> 00:13:40,010
<Default><b>It was during
that battle</b></Default>

250
00:13:40,350 --> 00:13:42,929
<Default><b>the awful one
against the third rebellion.</b></Default>

251
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:47,919
<Default><b>The battle where
my father died.</b></Default>

252
00:13:48,490 --> 00:13:50,059
<Default><b>[laughter]</b></Default>

253
00:13:50,169 --> 00:13:52,969
<Default><b>[JARALIS] If only he'd done
what he was supposed to.</b></Default>

254
00:13:53,129 --> 00:13:55,405
<Default><b>[JARALIS] If my plan
had come to fruition</b></Default>

255
00:13:55,429 --> 00:13:57,546
<Default><b>[JARALIS] I could have
restored my honor.</b></Default>

256
00:13:57,570 --> 00:13:58,806
<Default><b>[chattering]</b></Default>

257
00:13:58,830 --> 00:14:00,855
<Default><b>[JARALIS] But he just
happened to ride in</b></Default>

258
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:04,649
<Default><b>with his reinforcements and
figured that made him a hero.</b></Default>

259
00:14:05,750 --> 00:14:08,750
<Default><b>[♪ Tense music]</b></Default>

260
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:20,635
<Default><b>He stole the glory that
should have been mine.</b></Default>

261
00:14:20,659 --> 00:14:22,360
<Default><b>Over and over again!</b></Default>

262
00:14:24,580 --> 00:14:26,340
<Default><b>You will never
understand</b></Default>

263
00:14:26,539 --> 00:14:31,039
<Default><b>how much humiliation I endured
when your father was alive!</b></Default>

264
00:14:32,070 --> 00:14:35,005
<Default><b>He was always the bane
of my existence.</b></Default>

265
00:14:35,029 --> 00:14:36,069
<Default><b>So I...</b></Default>

266
00:14:37,139 --> 00:14:38,459
<Default><b>Don't tell me.</b></Default>

267
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,240
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

268
00:14:40,659 --> 00:14:43,379
<Default><b>[♪ Dramatic
music intensifies]</b></Default>

269
00:14:48,879 --> 00:14:49,976
<Default><b>[sword cutting sound]</b></Default>

270
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,120
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

271
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:54,716
<Default><b>Don't tell me!</b></Default>

272
00:14:54,740 --> 00:14:55,765
<Default><b>It's the truth.</b></Default>

273
00:14:55,789 --> 00:14:59,019
<Default><b>The only way to be rid of him
was to kill him myself.</b></Default>

274
00:15:04,299 --> 00:15:05,299
<Default><b>{\i1}Lucia.{\i0}</b></Default>

275
00:15:05,799 --> 00:15:06,799
<Default><b>{\i1}Fohl.{\i0}</b></Default>

276
00:15:08,009 --> 00:15:09,029
<Default><b>{\i1}Atla.{\i0}</b></Default>

277
00:15:12,730 --> 00:15:14,330
<Default><b>[sword cutting sound]</b></Default>

278
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:18,169
<Default><b>[♪ Somber music]</b></Default>

279
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:22,105
<Default><b>I can still remember
how incredible it felt to steal</b></Default>

280
00:15:22,129 --> 00:15:24,059
<Default><b>his glory-grabbing
life away.</b></Default>

281
00:15:24,299 --> 00:15:25,625
<Default><b>[JARALIS]
I'll never forget</b></Default>

282
00:15:25,649 --> 00:15:28,450
