285
00:15:33,090 --> 00:15:34,130
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

286
00:15:35,220 --> 00:15:37,190
<Default><b>Oh, that's the face!</b></Default>

287
00:15:37,419 --> 00:15:39,019
<Default><b>That's the face, yes!</b></Default>

288
00:15:39,049 --> 00:15:41,470
<Default><b>And it's exactly
like your father's!</b></Default>

289
00:15:42,039 --> 00:15:46,080
<Default><b>You and your father both provide
endless entertainment for me.</b></Default>

290
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:48,279
<Default><b>[FOHL] Shut up!</b></Default>

291
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:50,000
<Default><b>You bastard!</b></Default>

292
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,400
<Default><b>[evil giggle]</b></Default>

293
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:04,080
<Default><b>[bowel Sound]</b></Default>

294
00:16:05,590 --> 00:16:06,710
<Default><b>[startle]</b></Default>

295
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,816
<Default><b>It's the beast
transformation!</b></Default>

296
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:12,296
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

297
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,446
<Default><b>What's that?</b></Default>

298
00:16:13,470 --> 00:16:14,470
<Default><b>Well…</b></Default>

299
00:16:14,629 --> 00:16:18,049
<Default><b>There's a well-known legend
existing only within Siltvelt.</b></Default>

300
00:16:18,139 --> 00:16:19,666
<Default><b>[WERNER] Just like
a Demi-human</b></Default>

301
00:16:19,690 --> 00:16:22,115
<Default><b>can change into a beast man
to grow stronger</b></Default>

302
00:16:22,139 --> 00:16:25,620
<Default><b>the legend says that beast men
can transform as well.</b></Default>

303
00:16:26,879 --> 00:16:29,519
<Default><b>And you're telling me that's
what just happened?</b></Default>

304
00:16:31,970 --> 00:16:33,210
<Default><b>Most likely.</b></Default>

305
00:16:41,210 --> 00:16:43,010
<Default><b>The power is
overwhelming.</b></Default>

306
00:16:43,039 --> 00:16:44,839
<Default><b>It's more than
I imagined.</b></Default>

307
00:16:45,250 --> 00:16:47,005
<Default><b>With a power
such as this</b></Default>

308
00:16:47,029 --> 00:16:49,789
<Default><b>there'll never again be
a need for the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

309
00:16:50,110 --> 00:16:53,509
<Default><b>The whole world can just
worship me as a god instead!</b></Default>

310
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:01,830
<Default><b>Did he overcome
the poison?</b></Default>

311
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:04,319
<Default><b>[roar]</b></Default>

312
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,720
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Meteor Shield!</b></Default>

313
00:17:16,430 --> 00:17:18,509
<Default><b>Elder, Werner</b></Default>

314
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:22,679
<Default><b>[scream]</b></Default>

315
00:17:24,490 --> 00:17:26,390
<Default><b>[scream]</b></Default>

316
00:17:27,460 --> 00:17:28,529
<Default><b>Shit!</b></Default>

317
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:32,410
<Default><b>{\i1}Father, I promised.{\i0}</b></Default>

318
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:34,809
<Default><b>[♪ Gentle music]</b></Default>

319
00:17:38,890 --> 00:17:39,890
<Default><b>{\i1}Fohl!{\i0}</b></Default>

320
00:17:40,410 --> 00:17:41,825
<Default><b>{\i1}While I'm away{\i0}
{\i1}from home</b></Default>

321
00:17:41,849 --> 00:17:43,969
<Default><b>{\i1}you take care{\i0}
{\i1}of your mom and Atla.{\i0}</b></Default>

322
00:18:01,630 --> 00:18:04,019
<Default><b>{\i1}I'll protect them.{\i0}
{\i1}I promise you.{\i0}</b></Default>

323
00:18:10,259 --> 00:18:11,640
<Default><b>[roar]</b></Default>

324
00:18:13,420 --> 00:18:14,460
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

325
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:19,880
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

326
00:18:20,529 --> 00:18:21,889
<Default><b>{\i1}Back then, I...{\i0}</b></Default>

327
00:18:24,809 --> 00:18:26,289
<Default><b>[FOHL] {\i1}I was weak.{\i0}</b></Default>

328
00:18:30,269 --> 00:18:33,269
<Default><b>[♪ Gentle, sad music]</b></Default>

329
00:18:40,059 --> 00:18:42,019
<Default><b>[FOHL] {\i1}I couldn't
do anything.{\i0}</b></Default>

330
00:18:47,579 --> 00:18:49,079
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

331
00:18:51,519 --> 00:18:53,910
<Default><b>{\i1}I couldn't protect{\i0}</b></Default>

332
00:19:02,210 --> 00:19:03,650
<Default><b>[FOHL] {\i1}my mother.{\i0}</b></Default>

333
00:19:05,339 --> 00:19:07,940
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

334
00:19:08,170 --> 00:19:10,460
<Default><b>[battle scream]</b></Default>

335
00:19:13,109 --> 00:19:16,109
<Default><b>[♪ Gentle, sad
music continues]</b></Default>

336
00:19:24,650 --> 00:19:25,710
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

337
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:36,480
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

338
00:19:38,029 --> 00:19:39,029
<Default><b>[roar]</b></Default>

339
00:19:42,490 --> 00:19:43,740
<Default><b>[grunt]</b></Default>

340
00:19:49,779 --> 00:19:52,769
<Default><b>After you, I'm going after
that little sister of yours.</b></Default>

341
00:19:57,470 --> 00:19:58,920
<Default><b>Atla…</b></Default>

342
00:19:59,130 --> 00:20:00,970
<Default><b>[hard breathing]</b></Default>

343
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,740
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

344
00:20:05,910 --> 00:20:08,769
<Default><b>Time to die as a failure</b></Default>

345
00:20:09,029 --> 00:20:09,876
<Default><b>No! Fohl!</b></Default>

346
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:10,735
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

347
00:20:10,759 --> 00:20:11,839
<Default><b>Brother!</b></Default>

348
00:20:12,779 --> 00:20:14,059
