351
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:49,970
<Default><b>Oh my.</b></Default>

352
00:20:50,099 --> 00:20:51,186
<Default><b>Look at Fohl!</b></Default>

353
00:20:51,210 --> 00:20:53,410
<Default><b>He seems to be quite
manly out there.</b></Default>

354
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:55,180
<Default><b>And look</b></Default>

355
00:20:55,349 --> 00:20:56,349
