356
00:20:56,950 --> 00:20:58,310
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

357
00:20:59,069 --> 00:21:01,869
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Looks like his stats
have all gone way up.</b></Default>

358
00:21:03,119 --> 00:21:05,359
<Default><b>Is that from
the beast transformation?</b></Default>

359
00:21:08,990 --> 00:21:10,470
<Default><b>It's unbelievable.</b></Default>

360
00:21:10,759 --> 00:21:12,166
<Default><b>For two generations</b></Default>

361
00:21:12,190 --> 00:21:15,190
<Default><b>you and your family are still
getting in my way!</b></Default>

362
00:21:19,029 --> 00:21:24,859
<Default><b>[all angrily roaring]</b></Default>

363
00:21:26,799 --> 00:21:29,159
<Default><b>Is he really going
to destroy everything?</b></Default>

364
00:21:29,230 --> 00:21:31,390
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Raphtalia</b></Default>

365
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:32,509
<Default><b>Right!</b></Default>

366
00:21:32,619 --> 00:21:33,779
<Default><b>I'm on it.</b></Default>

367
00:21:34,279 --> 00:21:36,069
<Default><b>Hooray! It's Filo time!</b></Default>

368
00:21:36,210 --> 00:21:37,210
