369
00:21:39,329 --> 00:21:40,449
<Default><b>Let's go.</b></Default>

370
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:46,106
<Default><b>[TIRAN] {\i1}Fohl.{\i0}</b></Default>

371
00:21:46,130 --> 00:21:47,410
<Default><b>[LUCIA] {\i1}Fohl.{\i0}</b></Default>

372
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,280
<Default><b>Brother of mine.</b></Default>

373
00:21:57,789 --> 00:21:59,189
<Default><b>[FOHL] {\i1}Everyone.{\i0}</b></Default>

374
00:22:01,390 --> 00:22:02,510
<Default><b>{\i1}Watch me.{\i0}</b></Default>

375
00:22:04,970 --> 00:22:06,819
<Default><b>[♪ Closing music begins]</b></Default>

376
00:23:33,210 --> 00:23:35,339
